{"type":"message","id":"70878bf0","parentId":"25dbc04b","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:53:17.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full picture. The system has:\n\n1. **Memory pressure**: 3.7GB total, only 143MB free, 2.6GB used, swap is almost entirely used (3.9GB swap, 3.9GB used). This indicates severe memory exhaustion.\n\n2. **Top memory consumers**:\n   - `openclaw` (openclaw agent): 655MB RES (16.7%)\n   - `chrome` (running as root): 544MB RES (13.8%) - likely the browser running seller.tiktok.com\n   - Multiple other `chrome` processes: 152MB, 128MB, 103MB, 84MB, 82MB, 75MB - these add up\n   - `openviking`: 141MB\n   - `hermes`: 110MB\n   - `msedge`: 58MB\n   - `vibesurf`: 70MB\n\nThe swap is almost completely full (3.9GB used out of 3.9GB), and available memory is only 559MB. This is the likely cause of the slowness - when the system runs out of RAM, it starts swapping heavily, and with swap also nearly full, everything becomes extremely slow.\n\nThe `openclaw` process itself is consuming 655MB of memory, which seems quite high for an agent. I should report this to the user."},{"type":"text","text":"找到原因了。来看一下关键数据：\n\n**整机内存情况：**\n- 物理内存：3.7GB / 3.7GB（几乎用满）\n- Swap：3.9GB / 3.9GB（几乎用满）\n- 实际可用内存：约 560MB\n\n**主要内存消耗（按 RES 排序）：**\n| 进程 | 内存 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| openclaw | 656MB | 16.7% |\n| chrome（root） | 544MB | 运行 TikTok 后台那个 |\n| openviking | 141MB | |\n| hermes | 110MB | |\n| vibesurf | 70MB | |\n| msedge | 58MB | |\n\n另外还有 **6 个 chrome 子进程**，加起来也有几百 MB。\n\n---\n\n**结论：不是 vibesurf-1 容器本身的问题，是整个系统内存已经严重耗尽。**\n\nSwap 几乎满了（3.9GB 用了 3.9GB），系统处于极度的内存压力下，打开网页时触发换页会很慢，加载不出来就是这个原因。\n\n**建议：关掉一些不需要的 chrome 标签页/进程，或者 msedge，把物理内存腾出来。** 3.7GB 对开浏览器来说本来就很紧张。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timesta