{"type":"message","id":"1af0c3ef","parentId":"2d9c92b3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:55:10.032Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if there are many Chrome processes on the host machine. Let me clarify - yes, the `top` output showed multiple chrome processes running as root, all with very large VIRT memory (1392GB or 1393GB which is virtual memory, not RSS). These are child processes of the vibesurf-1 container's browser instance. Let me explain this more clearly."},{"type":"text","text":"对，看 `top` 输出的那个 `COMMAND` 列，全是 `chrome`：\n\n```\nroot ... chrome  (544MB RES)\nroot ... chrome  (152MB RES)\nroot ... chrome  (128MB RES)\nroot ... chrome  (103MB RES)\nroot ... chrome  (84MB RES)\nroot ... chrome  (82MB RES)\nroot ... chrome  (75MB RES)\n```\n\n一共 **7 个 chrome 子进程**，加起来至少 1GB+ 内存。\n\n这些都是 `vibesurf-1` 容器里跑的浏览器实例的子进程——你在 vibesurf 里每开一个标签页，宿主机上就会多一个 chrome 子进程。这些标签页积累下来，内存就被吃光了。\n\n你现在有哪些 chrome 进程在跑可以 kill 掉，或者直接在 vibesurf-1 的浏览器界面里把不用的标签页关掉。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776074098191,"responseId":"062bf0727a58e4c5483a765a9d7e6a71"}}
