{"type":"message","id":"50fe6ef8","parentId":"d3cc25f0","timestamp":"2026-04-13T11:00:59.201Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now the memory is much better:\n- Memory used: 1.8GB (down from 2.5GB)\n- Free: 919MB (up from 198MB)\n- Available: 1.3GB (up from 653MB)\n- Swap used: 3.3GB (down from 3.8GB)\n\nvibesurf-1 is now using only 231MB (down from 966MB), which means the chrome processes were indeed consuming ~700MB+.\n\nLet me report this to the user."},{"type":"text","text":"搞定。结果立竿见影：\n\n**清理前 → 清理后：**\n- 物理内存 free：198MB → **919MB**\n- 可用内存：653MB → **1.3GB**\n- Swap 使用：3.8GB → **3.3GB**\n- vibesurf-1 内存占用：966MB → **231MB**\n\n那些 chrome 进程加起来吃了 700MB+ 的内存，现在全清了。系统轻装上阵。\n\n---\n\n下一步要给 vibesurf-1 设定内存上限吗？设定一个合理的上限（比如 1.5GB）可以防止它再次把系统内存吃满。需要的话告诉我要设多少，我来改。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776078051637,"responseId":"062bffe4e3c02ce21ec029dee38a9c2a"}}
